-- Hindustan Petroleum's Choudhury Takes Helm as Chairman, Managing Director
-- Madelene Pearson
-- 2010-08-01T06:31:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-01/hindustan-petroleum-s-choudhury-takes-helm-as-chairman-managing-director.html

          
          
             Hindustan Petroleum Corp. said S. Roy
Choudhury had assumed charge as Chairman and Managing Director
at the state-owned refiner.  
 Choudhury, who was earlier Director-Marketing, replaces A.
Balakrishnan who retired yesterday, the Mumbai-based company
said in an e-mailed statement today.  
